{"tid":2383744,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人玩Arduino?","createTime":"2021-01-28T06:09:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-29T12:28:55.000Z","uid":292710,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9282451ab293161f18d967ab31bb61cf357d1fe6","tid":2383744,"uid":292710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T06:09:04.000Z","msg":"我岩岩用Arduino IDE 寫左個溫度計program<br />\n#include &lt;DS18B20.h&gt;<br />\n<br />\n#include &lt;DallasTemperature.h&gt;<br />\n#include &lt;OneWire.h&gt;<br />\n<br />\n#define ONE_WIRE_BUS D0                   <br />\n<br />\nOneWire oneWire(ONE_WIRE_BUS);<br />\n <br />\nDallasTemperature sensors(&amp;oneWire);           <br />\n<br />\nvoid setup(void)<br />\n{<br />\n  Serial.begin(115200); <br />\n  sensors.begin();<br />\n}<br />\n<br />\nvoid loop(void)<br />\n{ <br />\n  sensors.requestTemperatures();               <br />\n  Serial.println(&quot;Temperature: &quot;);<br />\n  delay(1000);<br />\n  Serial.println(sensors.getTempCByIndex(0));  <br />\n}"},{"pid":"141797ac281673da4c6e7e6eee3b2533d92f7f98","tid":2383744,"uid":14346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T11:57:24.000Z","msg":"得serial out嘅溫度計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n買幾隻七劃管兩粒595整埋standalone display啦"},{"pid":"a4f0884812b8115d3b3066da792d54a5f7086a5e","tid":2383744,"uid":98795,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T12:28:55.000Z","msg":"功課自己做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}